---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
const title = "Privacy | Cassady Tech Solutions";
const description = "Privacy information for Cassady Tech Solutions.";
---
<SiteLayout title={title} description={description} active="privacy">
	<section class="page-title"><div class="section-inner"><p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p><h1>Privacy Policy.</h1><p>This page explains how Cassady Tech Solutions handles information submitted through cassadytech.com.</p></div></section>
	<section class="section"><div class="section-inner content-block"><p><strong>Last updated:</strong> May 24, 2026</p><h2>Information collected</h2><p>When you use the contact form, Cassady Tech Solutions may collect the information you choose to provide, including your name, email address, phone number, company name, support area, and message. The site may also process basic technical information such as browser details, device information, IP address, referrer, and spam-prevention signals through hosting and security providers.</p><h2>How information is used</h2><p>Information submitted through the site is used to respond to requests, understand technical support needs, coordinate follow-up, prevent spam or abuse, protect the website, and maintain basic business records related to inquiries and service conversations.</p><h2>Form processing and service providers</h2><p>Contact form submissions are processed by a Cloudflare Worker API route. The form uses Cloudflare Turnstile to help reduce spam and automated abuse. Submissions are sent to the Cassady Tech Solutions inbox through Resend and may be forwarded to a configured workflow webhook for routing, follow-up, or customer relationship management.</p><h2>No sale of personal information</h2><p>Cassady Tech Solutions does not sell personal information submitted through this website. Information may be shared with service providers only as needed to host the site, secure the form, deliver email, route the inquiry, or support normal business operations.</p><h2>No public address</h2><p>Cassady Tech Solutions serves Southern Colorado and does not publish a public office address on this website.</p><h2>Contact</h2><p>Privacy questions can be sent to <a href="mailto:samuelc@cassadytech.com">samuelc@cassadytech.com</a> or discussed by phone at <a href="tel:+17197812356">719-781-2356</a>.</p><h2>Legal note</h2><p>This privacy policy is provided for general website notice purposes and should be reviewed by qualified counsel before being relied on as legal advice or a complete compliance program.</p></div></section>
</SiteLayout>
